---
// FAQ Section
---

<div id="faqs" class="bg-gray-50 py-16">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    
    <!-- Headline -->
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 text-center mb-12">
      FAQs â€” Swica vs Helsana
    </h2>

    <!-- FAQ Items -->
    <div class="space-y-4">
      
      <!-- FAQ 1 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden">
        <button class="w-full px-6 py-4 text-left flex items-center justify-between hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors" type="button" data-faq="1">
          <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Is SWICA better than Helsana for expats in Switzerland?</span>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-500 transform transition-transform faq-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" data-icon="1">
            <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </button>
        <div class="px-6 pb-4 text-gray-600 hidden faq-content" data-content="1">
          <p>Both are excellent for expats. SWICA excels in English customer service and satisfaction ratings (5.4/6 vs Helsana's 5.2/6). Helsana offers broader provider networks and more supplementary options. Choose SWICA for service-first experience, Helsana for network breadth. Premium differences are typically minimal.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ 2 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden">
        <button class="w-full px-6 py-4 text-left flex items-center justify-between hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors" type="button" data-faq="2">
          <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Which is cheaper: SWICA or Helsana health insurance?</span>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-500 transform transition-transform faq-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" data-icon="2">
            <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </button>
        <div class="px-6 pb-4 text-gray-600 hidden faq-content" data-content="2">
          <p>Premiums are similar for both providers, varying by canton, age, model, and deductible. Neither is consistently cheaper. SWICA might be slightly higher in some cantons, Helsana in others. Focus on service quality and supplementary benefits rather than basic premium differences.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ 3 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden">
        <button class="w-full px-6 py-4 text-left flex items-center justify-between hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors" type="button" data-faq="3">
          <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Can I switch from Helsana to SWICA for 2026?</span>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-500 transform transition-transform faq-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" data-icon="3">
            <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </button>
        <div class="px-6 pb-4 text-gray-600 hidden faq-content" data-content="3">
          <p>Yes, cancel your current Helsana policy by 30 November 2025 to switch to SWICA from 1 January 2026. Basic insurance switching is guaranteed. Supplementary insurance requires separate applications and may involve medical underwriting. Plan early for smooth transition.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ 4 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden">
        <button class="w-full px-6 py-4 text-left flex items-center justify-between hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors" type="button" data-faq="4">
          <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Do SWICA and Helsana offer English customer service?</span>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-500 transform transition-transform faq-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" data-icon="4">
            <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </button>
        <div class="px-6 pb-4 text-gray-600 hidden faq-content" data-content="4">
          <p>Both provide English support. SWICA is particularly praised for its dedicated English line and expat-friendly service quality. Helsana offers good English support through customer service and comprehensive English documentation. Both have English websites and app interfaces.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ 5 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden">
        <button class="w-full px-6 py-4 text-left flex items-center justify-between hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors" type="button" data-faq="5">
          <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Which health insurance has better digital services: SWICA or Helsana?</span>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-500 transform transition-transform faq-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" data-icon="5">
            <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </button>
        <div class="px-6 pb-4 text-gray-600 hidden faq-content" data-content="5">
          <p>Both offer excellent digital platforms. SWICA's mySwica app is highly rated for user-friendliness and claims processing. Helsana+ app provides comprehensive features and efficient digital submissions. Both support seamless online management and mobile claims processing.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ 6 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden">
        <button class="w-full px-6 py-4 text-left flex items-center justify-between hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors" type="button" data-faq="6">
          <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900">What are the main differences between SWICA and Helsana supplementary insurance?</span>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-500 transform transition-transform faq-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" data-icon="6">
            <polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </button>
        <div class="px-6 pb-4 text-gray-600 hidden faq-content" data-content="6">
          <p>SWICA offers generous wellness contributions (up to CHF 1,300/year with Completa Forte) and strong prevention focus through Optima plans. Helsana provides broader supplementary range including extensive international hospital coverage and comprehensive dental options. Both cover alternative medicine and offer premium supplementary plans.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</div>

<script is:inline>
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
    // Add click listeners to all FAQ buttons
    const faqButtons = document.querySelectorAll('[data-faq]');
    
    faqButtons.forEach(function(button) {
      button.addEventListener('click', function(e) {
        const target = e.currentTarget;
        const faqId = target.getAttribute('data-faq');
        const content = document.querySelector('[data-content="' + faqId + '"]');
        const icon = document.querySelector('[data-icon="' + faqId + '"]');
        
        if (content && icon) {
          if (content.classList.contains('hidden')) {
            content.classList.remove('hidden');
            icon.style.transform = 'rotate(180deg)';
          } else {
            content.classList.add('hidden');
            icon.style.transform = 'rotate(0deg)';
          }
        }
      });
    });
  });
</script>